<h1>Typography</h1>
<p>
  Localized typography involved working with fonts and
  handling the idiosyncracies of scripts.
</p>

<h2>Fonts</h2>
<p>
  We can use system fonts, universal font collections, or
  mixed per-language fonts.
</p>

